FuncDef: The display inof peer connection command displays information about the iNOF connection established between the local and peer devices after the iNOF reflector and client are configured. The display inof peer connection command displays information about the iNOF connection established between the local and peer devices after the iNOF reflector and client are configured. This command is supported only on the CE6860-SAN, CE6866K, CE6866, CE6860-HAM, CE6885-SAN, CE8850-SAN, CE8851K, CE8851-32CQ8DQ-P and CE8850-HAM.
